Package com.intellij.conversion

Class ProjectConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.conversion.ProjectConverter

  • public abstract class ProjectConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    Override some of 'create*Converter' methods to perform conversion. If none of these methods suits the needs, override isConversionNeeded(), getAdditionalAffectedFiles() and one of '*processingFinished' methods
